title: Vegan Food is Overpriced (really, most of it, in 2018)
description: This video is not about the excuse offered by some meat eaters that they imagine a vegan diet would be more expensive… it is, instead, about the doleful reality that vegans themselves live with: rip-off food prices.  Sadly, meat eaters are not wrong to regard the word "vegan" (where it appears on a label) as a pretext to raise prices: as with "organic" and "gluten free", that is too often the case.
